query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(ci t chn) NoMergeJoin(chn ci rt t mc) NoMergeJoin(chn ci mc rt t cn) NoMergeJoin(chn ci cn mc rt t ct) */ select min(chn.name) AS character,
min(t.title) AS movie_with_american_producer
from title AS t
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2009 AND ci.note like '%Marcy%'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id
inner join role_type AS rt
on rt.id = ci.role_id
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ci.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[gb]'
inner join company_type AS ct
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id;
